~= neutron-utils =~

A collection of utilities to make Neutron better.

- router.py -

usage: router.py [-h]
                 [--router-id ROUTER_ID | --tenant-id TENANT_ID | --network-id NETWORK_ID]

router.py - Utility to show routers and connected networks

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --router-id ROUTER_ID
                        Provides details for specified router
  --tenant-id TENANT_ID
                        Provides details of routers associated with specified
                        tenant
  --network-id NETWORK_ID
                        Provides details of routers connected to specified
                        network

- float.py -

usage: float.py [-h] [--network-id NETWORK_ID]

float.py - Utility to show floating IP consumption

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --network-id NETWORK_ID
                        Provides floating IP information for specified
                        external network
